odness, He grants him understanding of the religion. Verily, I am only a distributor, but Allah is the giver. Those within this nation will continue to establish the commandments of Allah. They will\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10923,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/03\/sahabah-aisha-knowledge\/","url_meta":{"origin":28579,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Aisha: Companions go to Aisha for answers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 3, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: We never had a problem occur to us, the companions of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, but that we would ask Aisha and find that she knew something about it. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3883 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0645\u064f\u0648\u0633\u064e\u0649 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31751,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/03\/sufyan-hadith-misguide-fiqh\/","url_meta":{"origin":28579,"position":5},"title":"Sufyan on Fiqh: Hadith cause misguidance, except for scholars of Fiqh","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Qayrawani reported: Sufyan ibn \u2018Uyaynah, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cThe prophetic Hadith cause misguidance, except for t